OL,3,CTougher crackdown on flytipping as
OL,4,Ccouncil introduces new street cameras
OL,6,FFly tippers could be caught more often
OL,7,Fas Walsall Council has introduced two
OL,8,FCCTV cameras to crack down on the
OL,9,Fcrime.
OL,11,FIt comes after local residents
OL,12,Fcomplained about a recent fly tipping
OL,13,Fincident in their neighbourhoods.
OL,15,FThese cameras are part of the
OL,16,Fcouncil's EnviroCrime plan, which aims
OL,17,Fto reduce illegal dumping by combining
OL,18,Feducation, enforcement and increased
OL,19,Fsurveillance.
