OL,3,CTougher crackdown on flytipping as
OL,4,Ccouncil introduces new street cameras
OL,6,FFlytipping is the illegal disposal of
OL,7,Fhousehold, industrial, commercial or
OL,8,Fother 'controlled' waste.
OL,10,FThe council has responded to a total
OL,11,Fof 787 reports about the crime in the
OL,12,Flast year. It says can go up to
OL,13,F#20,000 and offenders can even be sent
OL,14,Fto prison.
OL,16,FThe initiative uses many strategies,
OL,17,Fincluding:
OL,19,F- issuing warning letters
OL,21,F- offering advice on council services
