OL,3,CTougher crackdown on flytipping as
OL,4,Ccouncil introduces new street cameras
OL,6,FCouncillor Garry Perry, Leader of
OL,7,FWalsall Council says the measures are
OL,8,Fcrucial in the fight against
OL,9,Fflytipping:
OL,11,F"Since the installation of CCTV, there
OL,12,Fhave been no further incidents in the
OL,13,Fareas where the cameras were
OL,14,Finstalled."
OL,16,F"These measures are crucial in our
OL,17,Ffight against fly-tipping."
